## Common Issues

| Symptom | Likely cause | Fix |
|---|---|---|
| `400 Bad Request` from `signInWithIdp` | Google OAuth client not configured | Re-run Step 6 — JavaScript origins **must not** contain paths; redirect URIs **must** end in `/__/auth/handler` |
| User redirected to `/login` after sign-in | Redirect ran before session cookie was set | Verify `await createSessionCookie(result.user)` is called **before** `router.push("/dashboard")` (pitfall #22) |
| `FIREBASE_PRIVATE_KEY` parse error | Newlines not escaped | Ensure `.replace(/\\n/g, "\n")` in `firebase-admin.ts`, and that the env value contains literal `\n` sequences |
| `Server misconfigured: NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL not set` | CSRF guard env missing | Add `NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=http://localhost:3000` to `.env.local` |
| Session cookie name stripped on Firebase Hosting | Hosting strips non-`__session` cookies | Use the cookie name `__session` (already the default in this scaffold) |

Full pitfall reference (60 production issues):
→ [`references/09-common-pitfalls.md`](https://github.com/MangalaHQ/shipwithai-plugins/blob/main/plugins/auth/skills/auth-setup/references/09-common-pitfalls.md)

