## Production Checklist

- [ ] Set all `NEXT_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_*` and `FIREBASE_*` env vars in your hosting provider (Vercel/Netlify/etc.)
- [ ] Set `NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL` to your production URL (no trailing slash)
- [ ] Add production domain to **Firebase Console → Authentication → Settings → Authorized domains**
<!-- IF oauth=google -->
- [ ] Add production URLs to **Google Cloud Console → OAuth client → Authorized JavaScript origins** + **Redirect URIs**
- [ ] Submit OAuth consent screen for verification (or set to **In production**)
<!-- /IF -->
- [ ] Replace in-memory rate limiter with Upstash Redis for serverless deployments — see [`references/05-firebase-auth-guide.md` § Rate Limiting](https://github.com/MangalaHQ/shipwithai-plugins/blob/main/plugins/auth/skills/auth-setup/references/05-firebase-auth-guide.md#rate-limiting)
- [ ] Run `npx ts-node scripts/verify-auth-setup.ts` and confirm all checks pass

